	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=/db/poster.html?user=220331><span id= >Chasca</span></a><br><span id=notbold>3 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Can drop off pretty much from any mob in the East wing of Charasis. <br>We had it dropping from elementalbone skeletons, golems etc. And not minis, just plain trash mobs.<br>Drops very randomly.<br>There can be hours of none dropping and then suddenly several in a row or even from the same pull (provided you pull by 6 to 10 mobs). <br> <br>Lots of items drop off minis etc. that are ok for tribute. Lots of 50ties spells for all classes. And you can get your yearly supply of bone chips from there. ;) Main problem is soon no one has room for loot any more. As for xp, at lvl 65 it gives 1% of AA per kill. So not exactly fire or earth or KT level xp, but nevertheless you get something...<br>So your time is not totally wasted.<br><br>You can levi to East wing door (the stairs are fake) from the fire pot on South. But if your computer lags, you most probably fall into basement, have to run to teleport in the centre and try again. Can be frustrating. <br>So you can just go to the East wing via South (fake walls and secret passages; watch out for traps). South door can be picked open by a rogue with high lockpick skill or you have to have someone with<br><a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23020 target=akztarg>Hand of Glory</a> with you.<br>Btw, would be helpful if Hand of Glory was listed on Charasis quest list. ;)<br><br>Good luck with getting the essence.<br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Jul 19 03:01:45 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
